reviewText: "THE HIGH CHAPPARAL" WAS AN EXCELLENT T.V. SHOW, BIG JOHN AND HIS WIFE FACED MANY CHALLENGES, AND THE SHOW DID NOT SHY AWAY FROM THE GRITTY LIFE OF THE WEST. LOTS OF ACTION, BUT ALSO TENDER EMOTIONS AS WELL. JOHN WAS A TOUGH MAN, BUT HE DEEPLY LOVED HIS LOVELY SPANISH WIFE, VICTORIA. QUITE A TRENDSETTING SHOW!
